The '''Relephon Moons''' were in the [[Hapes Consortium/Legends|Hapes Consortium]], and [[Orbit/Legends|orbited]] the [[Gas giant/Legends|gas giant]] [[Relephon]]. The [[Moon/Legends|moons]], all of which were inhabited, had about thirty major and hundreds of smaller population centers. They were controlled by [[House AlGray]].

